# Historical context behind utelizing HoloLens in the context

The idea here was, to use Hololens as kind of a virtual device to walk through a production plant, and see  workstation KPIs in real time.
It was too time intensive at the time, and - although we had a HoloLens for Demo purposes - we could at the time not sell our ... pun SO intended ... vision.
I think the mentality of the folks back then wasn't there. They sort of loved it and found it useful. 
But honestly: I think it was a vain or a feeling embarresd thing.
They just could not agree, to let their employees running around with that thing. 🤷‍♂️ 
